One of my favourite watercolour paintings I’ve created. It’s a little special to me.
How does it make you feel?
What emotion does it evoke?

I am also interested to hear if there’s a certain animal you connect with more than others.
For me it’s always been horses... when I was little I would create countless hand drawn books about the adventures of unicorns and pegasus’s and watched probably every movie that has a horse in it 😂 at 23 years old I still pull over on the side of the road for pats when I see a horse in a paddock.

Horses randomly come to me in my dreams, and I wish to one day adopt one.

Good morning IG, I hope everyone had an enjoyable weekend! Today I wanted to share with you my latest aquatic millie scene jar. I have been loving making these after a long hiatus from making any jars. I used yellow blue dichro as the background, and over 45 chips on this one. It even has 3 triple layered millie marbs on the sides. It stands a little over 3.25” in height and is 3” in depth. The jar measured 46mm when put in the calipers. It is priced at $420. If anyone would like to acquire it please dibs below or shoot me a DM. Thanks!!
